Description: Native PlayXonotic launcher with login
 PlayXonotic launcher - sign in and play the native Xonotic game
 with your PlayXonotic account. Connects to playxonotic.com servers.
 Requires Xonotic (flatpak install org.xonotic.Xonotic).
